      <title>Version 0.1.4</title>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 18:02:23 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
<h2>New</h2>
<ul>
<li>Native Settings window - resolution, frame rate, bitrate, audio channels, HTTPS port, and packet size</li>
<li>Native About window</li>
</ul>
<h2>Changed</h2>
<ul>
<li>Connecting screen now shows a blurred box-art backdrop instead of flat black</li>
</ul>
      ]]></description>
