    <item>
      <title>Version 0.1.0</title>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 16:33:22 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>1</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
<h2>New</h2>
<ul>
<li>Initial native SwiftUI rewrite of the Moonlight/Sunshine client</li>
<li>Bonjour and manual host discovery</li>
<li>NVIDIA GameStream / Sunshine PIN pairing</li>
<li>Hardware H.264 decoding (VideoToolbox) and native Opus audio (AudioToolbox)</li>
<li>Keyboard and mouse input forwarding</li>
<li>Session background / resume support</li>
<li>In-app auto-updates via Sparkle</li>
</ul>
      ]]></description>
